# Android

## Apps

* ### Shader Editor
	<a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=de.markusfisch.android.shadereditor"><img class="Screenshot"
		src="screenshots/shader_editor.jpg" alt="Shader Editor"/></a>

	Create [GLSL](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/GLSL) shaders on
	your Android phone and use them as live wallpaper.

	<p class="Stats"><span>Created in <time datetime="2013-06">June 2013</time></span>$(loc ../ShaderEditor app/src/main)</p>

	+ [Google Play](https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=de.markusfisch.android.shadereditor)
	+ [GitHub](https://github.com/markusfisch/ShaderEditor)
	+ [Releases](https://github.com/markusfisch/ShaderEditor/releases)
* ### Binary Eye
	<a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=de.markusfisch.android.binaryeye"><img class="Screenshot"
		src="screenshots/binary_eye.jpg" alt="Binary Eye"/></a>

	1D and 2D barcode scanner for Android.

	<p class="Stats"><span>Created in <time datetime="2017-08">August 2017</time></span>$(loc ../BinaryEye app/src/main)</p>

	+ [Google Play](https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=de.markusfisch.android.binaryeye)
	+ [GitHub](https://github.com/markusfisch/BinaryEye)
	+ [Releases](https://github.com/markusfisch/BinaryEye/releases)
* ### Wave Lines Wallpaper
	<a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=de.markusfisch.android.wavelines"><img class="Screenshot"
		src="screenshots/wavelines.jpg" alt="Wave Lines Wallpaper"/></a>

