	<p class="Stats"><span>Created in <time datetime="2012-08">August 2012</time></span>$(loc ../WaveLinesWallpaper app/src/main)</p>

	+ [Google Play](https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=de.markusfisch.android.wavelines)
	+ [GitHub](https://github.com/markusfisch/WaveLinesWallpaper)
	+ [Releases](https://github.com/markusfisch/WaveLinesWallpaper/releases)
