## Components
* ### CameraView
	A view that shows what the camera sees.

	<p class="Stats"><span>Created in <time datetime="2017-08">August 2017</time></span>$(loc ../CameraView cameraview/src/main)</p>

	+ [GitHub](https://github.com/markusfisch/CameraView)
	+ [Releases](https://github.com/markusfisch/CameraView/releases)
* ### ScalingImageView
	ImageView that transforms its drawable according to touch input.

	<p class="Stats"><span>Created in <time datetime="2015-11">November 2015</time></span>$(loc ../ScalingImageView scalingimageview/src/main)</p>

	+ [GitHub](https://github.com/markusfisch/ScalingImageView)
	+ [Releases](https://github.com/markusfisch/ScalingImageView/releases)
* ### SwipeImageView
	Swipe/zoom/pinch ImageView.

	<p class="Stats"><span>Created in <time datetime="2017-01">January 2017</time></span>$(loc ../SwipeImageView swipeimageview/src/main)</p>

	+ [GitHub](https://github.com/markusfisch/SwipeImageView)
	+ [Releases](https://github.com/markusfisch/SwipeImageView/releases)
* ### Pie Menu
	A zooming pie menu.

	<p class="Stats"><span>Created in <time datetime="2013-09">September 2013</time></span>$(loc ../AndroidPieMenu src)</p>

	+ [GitHub](https://github.com/markusfisch/AndroidPieMenu)
* ### TouchClock
	Editable clock view.

	<p class="Stats"><span>Created in <time datetime="2013-09">September 2013</time></span>$(loc ../TouchClock src)</p>

	+ [GitHub](https://github.com/markusfisch/TouchClock)
